<h2>ABOUT AVIANNE &amp; CO.</h2>
<p><br /> World renowned as the largest single jewelry store in New York City's Diamond District.&nbsp;Since 1999, our store has been the home of various famous pieces of jewelry. Shop with us online and find out what it means to be a part of the Avianne family.&nbsp;</p>
<p><br />Visit us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/AvianneJewelers/">Facebook</a> or <a href="https://www.instagram.com/aviannejewelers/?hl=en">Instagram</a>.</p><br />
<p></p>
<p>We also invite you to visit our store. We are generally open to the public, however we often have celebrity clients who require the store to remain closed to the public, for media and security purposes. Please <a href="#dialog" id="contact-link">contact us</a> and set an appointment to ensure that we are available for in-store visits.</p>
